[
  {
    "startTime": 0.461,
    "endTime": 3.564,
    "text": "- Do you think that it is hard to be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.564,
    "endTime": 6.647,
    "text": "a rapper with your kind of skin tone?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.732,
    "endTime": 13.232,
    "text": "- What are you tryin' to say?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.922,
    "endTime": 24.202,
    "text": "- Can we open?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.202,
    "endTime": 25.452,
    "text": "- You can open."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.842,
    "endTime": 29.674999999999997,
    "text": "What's up?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.597,
    "endTime": 33.476,
    "text": "- I don't recognize you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.476,
    "endTime": 35.217999999999996,
    "text": "- Do you know who I am?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.218,
    "endTime": 36.051,
    "text": "- No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.165,
    "endTime": 39.998,
    "text": "- Are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.634,
    "endTime": 43.884,
    "text": "- Ryan Gosling."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.877,
    "endTime": 45.71,
    "text": "[laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.955,
    "endTime": 54.055,
    "text": "- Wow-ow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.055,
    "endTime": 55.107,
    "text": "- What is your job?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.107,
    "endTime": 56.725,
    "text": "- I am a musician."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.725,
    "endTime": 58.789,
    "text": "- Have you ever done a stage dive?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.789,
    "endTime": 60.549,
    "text": "- I've done many stage dives."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.549,
    "endTime": 62.418,
    "text": "- How many hours a week do you work?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.418,
    "endTime": 64.618,
    "text": "- Who's to say how much\r\nwork really tour is?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.618,
    "endTime": 66.189,
    "text": "You're really only on stage for like,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.189,
    "endTime": 68.098,
    "text": "an hour and a half a night."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.098,
    "endTime": 69.647,
    "text": "- And plus you're already just"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.647,
    "endTime": 71.967,
    "text": "restating the songs that you already made."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.967,
    "endTime": 74.397,
    "text": "- Right, is that even\r\nwork in the first place?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.397,
    "endTime": 76.41000000000001,
    "text": "Question mark. We don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.41,
    "endTime": 80.389,
    "text": "- Is there like song that you\r\nget like tired of singing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.389,
    "endTime": 83.755,
    "text": "- Yes, it's a song called Thrift Shop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.755,
    "endTime": 84.70899999999999,
    "text": "[Laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.709,
    "endTime": 85.56700000000001,
    "text": "- What school do you guys go to?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.567,
    "endTime": 86.39999999999999,
    "text": "- What's your favorite song?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.4,
    "endTime": 87.233,
    "text": "- Uh, McCleur."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.233,
    "endTime": 88.833,
    "text": "I got to McCleur and he goes to Hamilton."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.833,
    "endTime": 89.673,
    "text": "- You guys go to different schools."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.673,
    "endTime": 90.532,
    "text": "- Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.532,
    "endTime": 91.383,
    "text": "- Man back in the day,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.383,
    "endTime": 94.59299999999999,
    "text": "McCleur and Hamilton use\r\nto be kinda bad schools."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.593,
    "endTime": 95.82000000000001,
    "text": "- Oh, McCleur sucks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.82,
    "endTime": 96.732,
    "text": "- Does it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.732,
    "endTime": 97.565,
    "text": "- Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.565,
    "endTime": 98.812,
    "text": "- That's where I probably\r\nstarted to do drugs,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.812,
    "endTime": 100.503,
    "text": "was with McCleur kids man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.503,
    "endTime": 101.336,
    "text": "[Laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.713,
    "endTime": 105.071,
    "text": "Like actually for real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.071,
    "endTime": 107.583,
    "text": "I went to a McCleur\r\nparty, in seventh grade,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.583,
    "endTime": 109.15299999999999,
    "text": "and I think that was it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.153,
    "endTime": 112.983,
    "text": "- Why do you always use your\r\nhands when you talk, like well?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.983,
    "endTime": 114.553,
    "text": "- I rap, so like I."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.553,
    "endTime": 115.386,
    "text": "- Told ya!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.386,
    "endTime": 116.219,
    "text": "You do it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.219,
    "endTime": 118.372,
    "text": "- No I'm showing you,\r\nthis is like exaggerated,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.372,
    "endTime": 120.601,
    "text": "but like yeah, I rap."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.601,
    "endTime": 122.273,
    "text": "- Have you been recognized?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.273,
    "endTime": 124.303,
    "text": "- I got recognized on the way over here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.303,
    "endTime": 127.15299999999999,
    "text": "I was in Barnes and Nobel,\r\nsomeone stops me and says"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.153,
    "endTime": 130.27800000000002,
    "text": "\"Has anyone ever told you, that you look"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.278,
    "endTime": 132.025,
    "text": "a lot like Macklemore?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.025,
    "endTime": 135.10500000000002,
    "text": "So, normally I just say\r\nno, but today I said yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.105,
    "endTime": 138.53699999999998,
    "text": "And she said, \"I mean\r\nobviously you're not him.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.537,
    "endTime": 141.927,
    "text": "And in my mind I'm like,\r\ndoes she think I look older?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.927,
    "endTime": 143.595,
    "text": "I was thinking the other day that should"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.595,
    "endTime": 146.936,
    "text": "keep a wig in my glove\r\ncompartment of my car."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.936,
    "endTime": 149.274,
    "text": "I'm thinking like a brown kinda shag,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.274,
    "endTime": 151.345,
    "text": "maybe a weird hat, some sunglasses,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.345,
    "endTime": 152.785,
    "text": "I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.785,
    "endTime": 153.618,
    "text": "[laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.876,
    "endTime": 157.377,
    "text": "- When you wrote the song White Privilege,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.377,
    "endTime": 160.44500000000002,
    "text": "did you actually mean\r\nwhat you were saying?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.445,
    "endTime": 162.17499999999998,
    "text": "- Yeah, absolutely."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.175,
    "endTime": 163.977,
    "text": "The first version of White Privilege"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.977,
    "endTime": 165.665,
    "text": "I wrote when I was in college."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.665,
    "endTime": 167.748,
    "text": "It was 2005, so thirteen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.865,
    "endTime": 170.66500000000002,
    "text": "- That was three years before I was born."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.665,
    "endTime": 173.457,
    "text": "- Yeah, so it was thirteen years ago."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.457,
    "endTime": 177.876,
    "text": "Long time ago, and I was\r\nobserving a change in culture."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.876,
    "endTime": 179.26500000000001,
    "text": "It was an observation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.265,
    "endTime": 182.844,
    "text": "It was questioning what's\r\nmy place in this culture,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.844,
    "endTime": 185.594,
    "text": "and processing it through a song."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.796,
    "endTime": 189.95399999999998,
    "text": "- One of my favorite songs\r\nis the Immigrant Song."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.954,
    "endTime": 191.108,
    "text": "- Who sings that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.108,
    "endTime": 192.056,
    "text": "- Led Zeppelin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.056,
    "endTime": 192.977,
    "text": "- Mmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.977,
    "endTime": 194.217,
    "text": "- How do you not know that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.217,
    "endTime": 196.88600000000002,
    "text": "- Cause I listen to rap dude."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.886,
    "endTime": 198.756,
    "text": "- Since you're a rapper,\r\nlike you feel like"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.756,
    "endTime": 200.825,
    "text": "there's booze around you a lot, or?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.825,
    "endTime": 205.658,
    "text": "- Yeah, everywhere I go there's\r\njust a bottle Ciroc vodka."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.705,
    "endTime": 208.538,
    "text": "No, I'm just kidding."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.538,
    "endTime": 209.592,
    "text": "- Okay good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.592,
    "endTime": 212.14100000000002,
    "text": "- There is definitely a lot of alcohol"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.141,
    "endTime": 213.90099999999998,
    "text": "in the music industry in general,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.901,
    "endTime": 214.734,
    "text": "but it's been a really long time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.734,
    "endTime": 217.567,
    "text": "since I've had a drink of alcohol."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.498,
    "endTime": 219.331,
    "text": "- That's pretty good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.331,
    "endTime": 220.164,
    "text": "- Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.164,
    "endTime": 224.356,
    "text": "I think that what separates\r\nme from a normal person,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.356,
    "endTime": 229.253,
    "text": "is that when I put a drink\r\nor a drug into my body,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.253,
    "endTime": 231.82399999999998,
    "text": "it's like I have an\r\nallergic reaction to it,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.824,
    "endTime": 233.97500000000002,
    "text": "and I can't get enough of it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.975,
    "endTime": 237.392,
    "text": "So for me, any drug is a bad drug for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.716,
    "endTime": 241.215,
    "text": "- Where you on drugs once?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.215,
    "endTime": 242.156,
    "text": "- I was."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.156,
    "endTime": 242.989,
    "text": "- Mmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.989,
    "endTime": 245.124,
    "text": "- Oof, yeah. It's a long road back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.124,
    "endTime": 246.036,
    "text": "- Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.036,
    "endTime": 247.375,
    "text": "- Well Tommy, you wouldn't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.375,
    "endTime": 248.424,
    "text": "- Well yeah I wouldn't know,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.424,
    "endTime": 252.416,
    "text": "but I read all the like\r\npamphlets they give us in school."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.416,
    "endTime": 254.914,
    "text": "Don't do drugs kids, which\r\nis probably accurate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.914,
    "endTime": 256.139,
    "text": "- And you've listened."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.139,
    "endTime": 256.97200000000004,
    "text": "- Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.972,
    "endTime": 257.805,
    "text": "- Good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.805,
    "endTime": 260.079,
    "text": "- Can you still write\r\nmusic when you take drugs?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.079,
    "endTime": 262.97,
    "text": "- Music that's not very good, yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.97,
    "endTime": 264.85,
    "text": "- What's the most recent\r\ntime you've had a relapse?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.85,
    "endTime": 268.01800000000003,
    "text": "- Two years ago, it was bad, this is bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.018,
    "endTime": 268.851,
    "text": "- Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.851,
    "endTime": 270.066,
    "text": "- No it's fine, we can go there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.066,
    "endTime": 271.818,
    "text": "- No, no, no, if you don't want to."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.818,
    "endTime": 272.769,
    "text": "- No it's fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.769,
    "endTime": 275.26,
    "text": "There was a photo shoot,\r\nfor People Magazine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.26,
    "endTime": 277.599,
    "text": "I was told that we were\r\ngoing to be a like,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.599,
    "endTime": 279.099,
    "text": "50 sexiest people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.919,
    "endTime": 281.83,
    "text": "- Nice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.83,
    "endTime": 286.74699999999996,
    "text": "- It turns out, it was like 50\r\nsexiest like animal hunters."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.478,
    "endTime": 289.42,
    "text": "- You hunt, do you hunt?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.42,
    "endTime": 290.418,
    "text": "- Which is like a big difference."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.418,
    "endTime": 291.25100000000003,
    "text": "- Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.251,
    "endTime": 292.12899999999996,
    "text": "- Um, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.129,
    "endTime": 293.66,
    "text": "- Yeah, like great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.66,
    "endTime": 297.22,
    "text": "So I was very high, I think\r\nI passed out at some point."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.22,
    "endTime": 298.151,
    "text": "- Oh geez."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.151,
    "endTime": 299.42,
    "text": "- It was all bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.42,
    "endTime": 301.687,
    "text": "Anyway, that was the last time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.687,
    "endTime": 303.617,
    "text": "- What would you say your\r\nfavorite drink is now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.617,
    "endTime": 305.06,
    "text": "- You know what I really enjoy,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.06,
    "endTime": 308.539,
    "text": "is a fine chilled bottle of Martinelli's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.539,
    "endTime": 310.409,
    "text": "- That's delicious, the apple cider?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.409,
    "endTime": 312.311,
    "text": "- Yeah man.\r\n- Pretty good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.311,
    "endTime": 315.24899999999997,
    "text": "- Do you still have the\r\nsame passion for music"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.249,
    "endTime": 317.08200000000005,
    "text": "from when you started?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 321.949,
    "endTime": 326.949,
    "text": "- I'm having to think about it,\r\nso I would say probably not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.671,
    "endTime": 332.17199999999997,
    "text": "I don't know, it's a tough question."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.172,
    "endTime": 336.023,
    "text": "I feel like I'm kind of in a\r\ntransition point in my life,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.023,
    "endTime": 337.53900000000004,
    "text": "I wanna be a good dad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.539,
    "endTime": 338.709,
    "text": "- Do you have kids?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.709,
    "endTime": 339.54200000000003,
    "text": "- I do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339.542,
    "endTime": 340.375,
    "text": "- How many?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.375,
    "endTime": 341.615,
    "text": "- Two kids."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.615,
    "endTime": 343.623,
    "text": "You guys wanna see a\r\npicture of my daughter?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 343.623,
    "endTime": 345.175,
    "text": "- Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.175,
    "endTime": 346.925,
    "text": "- That's my new baby."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.382,
    "endTime": 351.902,
    "text": "- Do you think you're a good\r\nrole model to your fans?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.902,
    "endTime": 353.954,
    "text": "- It depends on the song."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 353.954,
    "endTime": 358.743,
    "text": "What I try to embody with\r\nmy music is being myself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 358.743,
    "endTime": 360.735,
    "text": "There's good versions of me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 360.735,
    "endTime": 363.314,
    "text": "and then there's the other person."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.314,
    "endTime": 366.644,
    "text": "I have kind of this, yin\r\nand yang type of thing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.644,
    "endTime": 368.034,
    "text": "to my personality."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 368.034,
    "endTime": 372.111,
    "text": "So, depending on the song,\r\nyou might get either version."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372.111,
    "endTime": 373.553,
    "text": "It's true to who I am, and other people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 373.553,
    "endTime": 374.535,
    "text": "can relate to it too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.535,
    "endTime": 375.653,
    "text": "We're not perfect,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 375.653,
    "endTime": 378.36400000000003,
    "text": "there's days where you're\r\nprobably a great kid,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 378.364,
    "endTime": 380.20399999999995,
    "text": "and there's day where\r\nsometimes your parents are like"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 380.204,
    "endTime": 381.204,
    "text": "\"Oh my God.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 382.7,
    "endTime": 386.56399999999996,
    "text": "Maybe. Maybe you're just great\r\nall the time, I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 386.564,
    "endTime": 387.39700000000005,
    "text": "- Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.397,
    "endTime": 388.23,
    "text": "- Are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389.065,
    "endTime": 389.898,
    "text": "- Kind of."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389.898,
    "endTime": 392.10200000000003,
    "text": "- See what I'm saying,\r\nsee what I'm saying?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392.102,
    "endTime": 395.426,
    "text": "- Do you guys have any ideas in terms of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 395.426,
    "endTime": 399.34299999999996,
    "text": "song, or songs, or album, or\r\nconcepts, or any sort of idea"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 399.343,
    "endTime": 402.591,
    "text": "that I should put in to my music?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.591,
    "endTime": 404.442,
    "text": "- Honestly no, cause like you've been"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 404.442,
    "endTime": 407.322,
    "text": "doing pretty good by yourself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.322,
    "endTime": 409.51,
